@page "/components/link"

<PageHeader Title="Link 链接">
    文字超链接用于跳转一个新页面，如当前项目跳转，友情链接等。
</PageHeader>

<Example Title="文字链接">
    <Description>最简单的文字链接形式，点击后直接跳转到对应链接。</Description>
    <RunContent>
        <Link>跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Primary">跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Warning">跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Success">跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Danger">跳转链接</Link>
    </RunContent>
    <CodeContent>
        @Code.Create(@"
```html
<Link>跳转链接</Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Primary"">跳转链接</Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Warning"">跳转链接</Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Success"">跳转链接</Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Danger"">跳转链接</Link>
```
")
    </CodeContent>
</Example>
<Example Title="下划线文字链接">
    <Description>在文字下加横线，表明此处为链接。</Description>
    <RunContent>
        <Link Underline>跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Primary" Underline>跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Warning" Underline>跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Success" Underline>跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Danger" Underline>跳转链接</Link>
    </RunContent>
    <CodeContent>
        @Code.Create(@"
```html
<Link Underline>跳转链接</Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Primary"" Underline>跳转链接</Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Warning"" Underline>跳转链接</Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Success"" Underline>跳转链接</Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Danger"" Underline>跳转链接</Link>
```
")
    </CodeContent>
</Example>
<Example Title="带图标的链接">
    <Description>最简单的文字链接形式，点击后直接跳转到对应链接。</Description>
    <RunContent>
        <Link><Icon Name="IconName.Edit"/> 跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Primary"><Icon Name="IconName.Edit" /> 跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Warning"><Icon Name="IconName.Edit"/> 跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Success">跳转链接 <Icon Name="IconName.Home" /></Link>
        <Link Theme="Theme.Danger">跳转链接 <Icon Name="IconName.Gift" /></Link>
        <br />

        <Link Underline><Icon Name="IconName.Edit" /> 跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Underline Theme="Theme.Primary"><Icon Name="IconName.Edit" /> 跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Underline Theme="Theme.Warning"><Icon Name="IconName.Edit" /> 跳转链接</Link>
        <Link Underline Theme="Theme.Success">跳转链接 <Icon Name="IconName.Home" /></Link>
        <Link Underline Theme="Theme.Danger">跳转链接 <Icon Name="IconName.Gift" /></Link>
    </RunContent>
    <CodeContent>
        @Code.Create(@"
```html
<Link><Icon Name=""IconName.Edit""/> 跳转链接</Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Primary""><Icon Name=""IconName.Edit""/> 跳转链接</Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Warning""><Icon Name=""IconName.Edit""/> 跳转链接</Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Success"">跳转链接 <Icon Name=""IconName.Home"" /></Link>
<Link Theme=""Theme.Danger"">跳转链接 <Icon Name=""IconName.Gift"" /></Link>

<br />

<Link Underline><Icon Name=""IconName.Edit""/> 跳转链接</Link>
<Link Underline Theme=""Theme.Primary""><Icon Name=""IconName.Edit""/> 跳转链接</Link>
<Link Underline Theme=""Theme.Warning""><Icon Name=""IconName.Edit""/> 跳转链接</Link>
<Link Underline Theme=""Theme.Success"">跳转链接 <Icon Name=""IconName.Home"" /></Link>
<Link Underline Theme=""Theme.Danger"">跳转链接 <Icon Name=""IconName.Gift"" /></Link>
```
")
    </CodeContent>
</Example>
